text: What should we have for dinner...?

Maybe going to a restaurant would be safe.
We didn't make bento today.

Even if I were to make it,
it would take time to return to the office and prepare.

How about the concession stand!
Since we came to the plaza to play!

I think that's a good idea...
Yakisoba or takoyaki sounds fun...

Yeah, let's do that.
Then we'll just have to find the concession stand.
